---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tenable Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">

<div class="flex items-center gap-6">

<img src="/logos/tenable.png" class="h-10" alt="Tenable">

<div>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Tenable
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
Vulnerability management and continuous risk-based security for modern IT and cloud environments.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Core Products
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Tenable.io</li>
<li>• Nessus Professional</li>
<li>• Tenable.sc</li>
<li>• Vulnerability Management Services</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Capabilities
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Asset discovery and vulnerability scanning</li>
<li>• Risk-based prioritization</li>
<li>• Cloud and container security</li>
<li>• Compliance reporting</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Use Cases
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Continuous vulnerability assessment</li>
<li>• Prioritizing remediation based on business risk</li>
<li>• Securing cloud workloads and containers</li>
<li>• Compliance and audit readiness</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Why Tenable
</h2>

<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
Tenable provides comprehensive visibility into vulnerabilities across IT and cloud assets, enabling risk-informed remediation.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>
